Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明年的秋天不知能不能看得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳是早睡的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,星月是熬夜的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚之前结束所有祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,耶鲁节之夜就要来临啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你好呀 夜之宠儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,人之子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好过耶鲁节了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,耶鲁节？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正要做耶鲁节的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.64,0:02:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亚斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,贪睡虫 夜晚很快就来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要烧耶鲁原木
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.84,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在黑色女神和冥府之鹿踏上荒野之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好 艾利亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那俩孩子是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,耶鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们通常是在冬至这天到来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我叫他们耶鲁双子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过实际情况我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天会很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.52,0:02:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,身体难受要说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不配做使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,智世陷入危险时我什么都做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他这段时间一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs55}我这使魔做得毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该比我对智世更知根知底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,智世会隐瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能也跟着羞于启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,以后还是早点跟我说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.70,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我还能想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,智世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为刚从外面回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.78,0:03:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来为耶鲁节做准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.24,0:05:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是“美”？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.35,0:05:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.18,0:05:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,有个在榭寄生下可以接吻的习俗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他看来很想试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你能弯下腰来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,背后？ 腰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有点痒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.33,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,路兹也来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.03,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那进去吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.02,0:06:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好的老爷 我收下了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉每次给你的时间都很急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别客气 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在 没问题 我留了字条了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,告辞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,人好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,智世 我躲到里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉大老远把你叫到伦敦来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,耶鲁节礼物是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给连富烈德先生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的只是不知送他什么好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,之前送了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,之前…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,反倒是他送我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,所以今年我想回赠他些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,吃了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不送那块头骨什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,都没想过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就是我俩一起找礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是铁了心要拖上我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,找到好东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这得看各人喜好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.48,0:09:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,说来我就不知道他有什么喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我没送过别人礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的人不多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没认识什么可以送礼物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那我和智世就是伙伴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法和魔术虽有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.46,0:09:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们各自跟随师父学习并生存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哟 这不是恩滋华斯老爷家的小姑娘嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,黑泽尔先生你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,智世 你在和谁说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友这…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,魔术师和魔法使不同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给自己施了障眼法 他们是注意不到我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.35,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那选一件能让你想象他在使用的样子的东西如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:10:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想一下和他有关的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑一下觉得自然的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再转一圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.28,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,平时会用的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到一个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,狡猾啊 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能学我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是爱丽丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,像以前那样一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.62,0:11:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不吸了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哪…哪冒出来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,走！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的黑历史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,药味道好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一点不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是因为喜欢才吸的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在想来都像是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这事儿很没劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,算了不说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.32,0:12:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我那废物父母吸毒成瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能做药贩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是老师把我捡回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到那个金发小鬼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,得给她点教训
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你看什么看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你干什…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你想一直待在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没自我介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫米哈伊尔·连富烈德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么叫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.26,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,先洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我还完全不信任老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.46,0:14:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对之前一直生活在社会阴暗角落的我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要信任别人太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但那天…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看不懂标题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都跟你说了不能打开！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不 也是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,早跟你说清楚就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.04,0:15:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.55,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但还好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好不容易精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不该再受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这种我处理得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.92,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说是无师自通的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.54,0:16:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我会好好做的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个保镖 我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,下次就有劳你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想起来都觉得难过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.97,0:17:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,智世不用想那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.87,0:17:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,自己幸不幸福是自己决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.74,0:17:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你听我讲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对了你们那儿有小鸟信使去过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,蛮小的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那我会再写信给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你陪我到这么晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我也要谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,希望我们都能顺利送出礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊 交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你这哥哥觉得她合格了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是个坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.31,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史黛拉 伊森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 艾利亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么 都跑伦敦去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,还和连富烈德的弟子一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你想想你都遇到几次危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.90,0:18:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,还偷偷溜出门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.01,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你不会同意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不会同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:18:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别太生气了艾利亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,生气？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我在生气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我是去买…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然早了一天 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亚斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到你会送我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没想过会送你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 艾利亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 我看你总是带同一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就想你或许是带着它心安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你要是不喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也送智世一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只给安洁莉卡她们做过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,想着也给智世做一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.72,0:20:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.34,0:20:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亚斯做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,以前安洁莉卡要我做过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,说是要一个熊玩偶做礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得今年做的这个是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你之后一直在做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道其他的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我在上面设置了点机关
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那是大家送你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,安洁莉卡 赛门 林德尔也送了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.70,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当然礼物应该是当天送的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以留着明天开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:20:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 先吃晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,说教等吃好再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,原来他没忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你说了我就会跟着去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以买很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这我就有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,女孩子之间有点小秘密的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,圣诞节就是这样的感觉…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信我竟然会这样期待明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这可怜的孩子啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//----------------------------OST----------------------------
Comment: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------NEXT----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.11,0:23:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,古老生物 灰眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:24:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,被经历悠长时光的他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,玩弄的姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法使和少女会为姐弟俩出手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.93,0:24:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我！ 那是我的弟弟！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//----------------------------END----------------------------
